
IRSA  (IAMRole in Service Account)
=============
The kubernates objects pods will talk with AWS services like S3, EBS, DynamoDB , it required CSI drivers along with pod identity or IRSA.

IRSA will make use of OIDC (OpenID connect) for the authentication and utherization by a token system. 

kubernates cluster having OIDC url . It represents kubernates API server identity system. 

we are attaching OIDC uel to the IAM role , when ever aws sends tokens to the OIDC it will accept by the IAM. 

AWS-STS - security token service (this will provide token when ever authentcation required)

